Honest review from one of SKIN1004's employees👀:

“It was about 3 month before I joined the company, I was hanging out with a friend of mine and she brought me the Madagascar Centella Ampoule as a present saying it was her latest find. I thanked her and accepted it as an act of politeness. To be honest, I was skeptical. 

I have a skin condition called rosacea and super sensitive and fair skin. All of my skincare products have been prescribed by my dermatologist and I haven’t tried any other brands for years. I was in remission and was happy about it.

That day I came home, put the ampoule in my drawer and forgot about it. Then couple of weeks later I had a “selfcare-day” and decided to try it. Next morning while looking in the mirror I didn’t notice any irritation, allergies or new pimples. To my surprise my skin “accepted” the ampoule.

After trying it for a week I've developed my own method of using it. After cleansing and exfoliating, I simply apply a GENEROUS amount of it. Wait till my skin absorbs it, and then just go to sleep. It keeps my skin hydrated through the night, heals blemish spots and itchiness.

To my surprise after a couple of months, I received a job offer from SKIN1004 but that's a whole different story. Yesterday I finished my third bottle and am going to open a new one today”.

Writing style and punctuation of the author has been preserved.

SKIN1004 - our brand story, #the_BEGINNING

Getting such warm feedback from you inspired us to tell you more about ourselves and share all the insides of SKIN1004✊. We’ll post a series of stories where we’ll share to you all the details about what SKIN1004 means, why we've chosen Madagascar Centella, and the story behind it all. 

To begin with, let’s start with our slogan “DELIVERING YOU THE UNTOUCHED NATURE” and its connection to our brand ingredient Centella Asiatica.

We believe that whatever that touches the skin must be clean, and with that, the 'ingredient' is the most priority to think about. It's so important to know what is applied to your skin and the ingredients and where they're from. Though it may be obvious, as a skincare brand, we want to find the best ingredient that is suitable for everyone. An ingredient that is mild and gentle, so that everyone can approach skincare with ease. 

After much effort, we have arrived at Madagascar, the oldest island on Earth🌎, with 170 million years of the most ancient and pristine nature. From the ancient wisdom of natives, we found healing and protective properties of Centella Asiatica, also known as the leaf that brings life. That’s when we decided to use it as the main ingredient for all of our products.

...to be continued…

A Boosting Shot is the first step in your skincare routine — preparing your skin to better absorb everything that comes next. But not all boosters work the same.

What sets this one apart is spicule technology — a micro-delivery system. These microscopic needle-like structures create tiny pathways on the skin’s surface that helps active ingredients penetrate deeper and absorb more effectively. In short, it’s not just about what’s in the formula — it’s about how your skin receives it.

SKIN1004 LAB IN NATURE’s Boosting Shot Spicule is powered by:

1️⃣ Centella Asiatica — to calm irritation, strengthen the skin barrier, and support visible recovery
2️⃣ Panthenol (Pro-Vitamin B5) — to deeply hydrate and help reinforce a healthy, resilient barrier

Together, they deliver fast-acting soothing and repair. And with spicules guiding them beneath the surface, this booster sets the stage for real, lasting transformation — starting from within.

LAB IN NATURE
Available now at skin1004.com.

WHERE NATURE MEETS PRECISION.

We looked deeper into nature’s potential —
not just to find its purity, but to understand its power.
And to deliver that power to the skin, 
in its most thoughtful and optimized form.

We study and refine nature —not to change its essence,
but to deliver its purest ingredients in their most effective way.
We hope to deliver nature’s strengths with delicacy and precision.

LAB IN NATURE
Available now at skin1004.com.

LAB_Expansion

LAB IN NATURE observes nature not only at its surface, but with depth and intention — studying the ingredients discovered through close, meticulous exploration. This process of looking deeper mirrors the act of peering through a microscope in a lab — where the unseen becomes visible to discover the invisible world that lies within.

Using the visual metaphor of the microscope lens, its path of light, and the magnified imagery that results, we translate this perspective into a graphic system: an experimental grid laid over organic curves, representing nature as seen through a lens — refined, refracted, and revealed.

These visuals symbolize a message — a perspective which we explore nature with clarity and precision.

LAB IN NATURE is not about capturing what nature simply appears to be. It is about uncovering what nature truly is — through deep observation, thoughtful inquiry, and a commitment to honest, purposeful skincare.

LAB IN NATURE
